3%\n|-\n|}\n\n==FIFA rankings history==\nMontenegro national football team is present on [[FIFA rankings]] since June 2007. Until now, best ranking of Montenegro was 16th place in the world (June 2011).<br />\nBelow is a chronological list of Montenegro position on FIFA ranking-list by every three months, with number of points.\n\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-4}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! List / month\n! Pos\n! Pts\n|-\n| June 2007\n| '''199'''\n| ''0''\n|-\n| September 2007\n| '''186'''\n| ''21''\n|-\n| December 2007\n| '''172'''\n| ''65''\n|-\n| March 2008\n| '''175'''\n| ''65''\n|-\n| June 2008\n| '''142'''\n| ''180''\n|-\n| September 2008\n| '''136'''\n| ''198''\n|-\n| December 2008\n| '''112'''\n| ''310''\n|-\n| March 2009\n| '''112'''\n| ''310''\n|-\n| June 2009\n| '''110'''\n| ''331''\n|-\n| September 2009\n| '''89'''\n| ''380''\n|-\n| December 2009\n| '''74'''\n| ''456''\n|-\n| March 2010\n| '''69'''\n| ''494''\n|-\n| June 2010\n| '''64'''\n| ''500''\n|-\n| September 2010\n| '''40'''\n| ''684''\n|-\n| December 2010\n| '''25'''\n| ''824''\n|}\n{{col-4}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! List / month\n! Pos\n! Pts\n|-\n| March 2011\n| '''25'''\n| ''824''\n|-\n| June 2011\n| '''16'''\n| ''915''\n|-\n| September 2011\n| '''26'''\n| ''777''\n|-\n| December 2011\n| '''51'''\n| ''585''\n|-\n| March 2012\n| '''44'''\n| ''601''\n|-\n| June 2012\n| '''50'''\n| ''581''\n|-\n| September 2012\n| '''48'''\n| ''606''\n|-\n| December 2012\n| '''31'''\n| ''756''\n|-\n| March 2013\n| '''28'''\n| ''790''\n|-\n| June 2013\n| '''25'''\n| ''841''\n|-\n| September 2013\n| '''27'''\n| ''766''\n|-\n| December 2013\n| '''52'''\n| ''594''\n|-\n| March 2014\n| '''46'''\n| ''639''\n|-\n| June 2014\n| '''51'''\n| ''574''\n|-\n| September 2014\n| '''43'''\n| ''591''\n|}\n{{col-4}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! List / month\n! Pos\n! Pts\n|-\n| December 2014\n| '''59'''\n| ''537''\n|-\n| March 2015\n| '''67'''\n| ''531''\n|-\n| June 2015\n| '''70'''\n| ''513''\n|-\n| September 2015\n| '''77'''\